{"tid":2374588,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"華春瑩: Twitter不要顯示雙重標準 中方須說明真相","createTime":"2021-01-21T10:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T11:08:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3728958ad91fac3022542e9bf7026d8b2c4719fd","tid":2374588,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:46:10.000Z","msg":"外交部發言人華春瑩說，已注意社交媒體Twitter，對中國駐美使館帳戶採取限制措施，中方對此存在關注，呼籲Twitter不要顯示雙重標準。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter早前封鎖中國駐美國大使館的帳戶，理由是帳戶發布了一篇有關中國新疆政策的推文，以反駁美方說法。美國指控中國壓迫新疆維吾爾人，犯下種族滅絕和反人類罪行，中方批評有個別反華反共勢力，以人權為幌子干涉中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩說在美國社交媒體上，存在大量陰謀論及虛假資訊，並非常活躍，美國本身亦受到負面及嚴重的影響；又說網上有很多針對中國的虛假及炒作資訊，中國使館當然有責任和義務澄清，說明真相。她希望Twitter秉持客觀公正，不要在有關問題上顯示雙重標準或加強甄別。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571642-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571642-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcBY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=0f7b1259\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571642-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=49264ac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571642-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"83721fe6254397532babee437cef7b9039e964bb","tid":2374588,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcd7e0fc99dfb4823ea17da252a37dc2b701c52","tid":2374588,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa475600a0c94a3ebefe99e6208c20d5a047afb","t